<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>アルバイト履歴書</title>
    <!-- Bootstrap CSS -->
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <!-- Custom CSS -->
    <!--    <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css">-->
</head>
<body>
<div class="container resume-container">
    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-6">
            <h1 class="resume-title">アルバイト履 歴 書</h1>
        </div>
        <!--        <div class="col-4 text-center">-->
        <!--            <div class="date-box">-->
        <!--                <span>年</span>-->
        <!--                <span>月</span>-->
        <!--                <span>日</span>-->
        <!--            </div>-->
        <!--        </div>-->
        <div class="col-4 text-end">
            <span class="d-block title">年 月 日　現在</span>
            <span class="d-block sub-title"> yyyy/mm/dd as of now</span>
        </div>
        <div class="col-2 text-end">
            logo morikosan
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Main Content -->
    <div class="row">
        <!-- Left Column -->
        <div class="col-md-10">
            <div class="form-section p-0" style="border-bottom: unset;">
                <div class="form-group p-0" style="border-bottom: 1px dashed;">
                    <label>
                        <span class="d-block title">
                            フリガナ
                        </span>
                        <span class="d-block sub-title">
                            Furigana
                        </span>
                    </label>
                    <div class="form-input"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="form-group p-0">
                    <label>
                        <span class="d-block title">
                            名 前
                        </span>
                        <span class="d-block sub-title">
                            Name
                        </span>
                    </label>
                    <div class="form-input"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="form-group p-0">
                    <label>
                        <span class="d-block title">
                            国 籍
                        </span>
                        <span class="d-block sub-title">
                            Nationality
                        </span>
                    </label>
                    <div class="form-input"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="form-group p-0">
                    <label>
                        <span class="d-block title">
                           生年月日
                        </span>
                        <span class="d-block sub-title">
                            Date of birth
                        </span>
                    </label>
                    <div class="birth-date form-input ">
                        <span>    年</span>
                        <span>月</span>
                        <span>日 </span>
                        <span>(満   歳)</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Right Column -->
        <div class="col-md-2">
            <div class="photo-section">
                <div class="photo-box">
                    <p>写真 ID Photo (30mm×40mm)</p>
                    <p>写真の裏面に、名前、学校名を書いてください。</p>
                    <p>Please write your name and name of school/university on the back.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div id="header__end">
        <div class="row header__end__address">
            <div class="col-md-12">
                <div class="form-section p-0">
                    <div class="form-group p-0">
                        <label>
                            <span class="d-block title">
                                住 所
                            </span>
                            <span class="d-block sub-title">
                                Address
                            </span>
                        </label>
                        <div class="form-input"></div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row header__end__tel">
            <div class="col-md-3 col-left">
                <div class="form-section">
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label>
                            <span class="d-block title">
                                電話番号
                            </span>
                            <span class="d-block sub-title">
                                Tel
                            </span>
                        </label>
                        <div class="form-input"></div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-9 col-right">
                <div class="form-section">
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label style="height: 65px; display: flex; align-items: center;">
                            <span class="d-block">E-mail</span>
                        </label>
                        <div style="display: flex; align-items: center;">
                            <span class="d-block">@</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row header__end__residence">
            <div class="col-md-5 col-left">
                <div class="form-section" style="border-bottom: 1px solid black">
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label>
                            <span class="d-block title">
                                在留資格
                            </span>
                            <span class="d-block sub-title">
                                Status of residence
                            </span>
                        </label>
                        <div class="form-input"></div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-7 col-right">
                <div class="form-section" style="border-bottom: 1px solid black">
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label>
                            <span class="d-block title">在留期限</span>
                            <span class="d-block sub-title">Period of stay</span>
                        </label>
                        <div class="">
                            <span class="d-block">年     月    日   まで有効</span>
                            <span class="d-block sub-title">*Valid until yyyy/mm/dd</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Education/Employment Section -->
    <div class="section-title mt-4">
        <span class="title" style="margin-right: 20px">母国・日本での　学歴 ／ 職歴 ／ 受賞歴 </span>
        <span class="sub-title">Education history / Employment history / Awards received (in your home country & in Japan)</span>
    </div>
    <div class="large-input"></div>

    <!-- Qualifications Section -->
    <div class="section-title" style="border-top: unset">
        <span  class="title" style="margin-right: 20px">資格 ／ 免許 </span>
        <span class="sub-title">Qualifications / Licenses</span>
    </div>
    <div class="large-input"></div>

    <!-- Footer Notes -->
    <div class="notes mt-4">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-1">注意:</div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div>1.黒いボールペンで書く</div>
                <div>2.全て日本語で書く（外国の学校名などはカタカナまたは英語で書く）</div>
                <div>3.※マークがついているところは◯をつける</div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div>1.Please write with a black ballpen.</div>
                <div>2.Please write everything in Japanese.<br>
                    (Names of schools may be written either in katakana or English)
                </div>
                <div>3.Please circle the applicable option for section with ※</div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
